RESULTS
INaCa and INaK increase in magnitude with
increasing [Na1]i

An important step in investigating the effects of elevated
[Na1]i on the electrical and contractile properties of the
myocyte is to characterize its effect on processes that reg-
ulate ionic concentrations. Two important ion transporters
that are affected by alterations in [Na1]i are INaCa and INaK.

